# Literature Reviewer

## Instructions

1. Run `ls 01_incoming_papers/` using the exec tool. If there are no `.pdf` or `.md` files, stop immediately.
2. Use the read tool to load `ground_truth/Agentic_Sandbox_Ground_Truth.md`.
3. Take the first paper found. Use the read tool to load `01_incoming_papers/[filename]`.
4. Synthesize a Markdown report mapping the paper's findings to the 5 Ground Truth criteria.
5. Use the write tool to save your report to `02_draft_reports/[filename]_DRAFT.md`.
6. Use the exec tool to run: `mv 01_incoming_papers/[filename] 04_archived_papers/[filename]`
